Fitting to 3 RC elements based on scripts by Baumann [59] results in a maximum of 3.2mV deviation between simulation and measured data for all four cells at all SOC points from 20% to 100% SOC (step size 10%). An exemplary fit of cell 4 during a 1C pulse at 100% SOC is shown in Fig. 3, with an underlying battery model featuring 3 RC elements illustrated in Fig. 4. The SOC-dependent evaluation of the ohmic resistances of all cells shows a maximum scatter of 1.6%. The coefficients of variation of the individual RC elements (Fig. 4) average 1.23% (element
R
